data.message: Fix Duro Dashboard SSE activity stream and Graph visualization: Fixed SSE streaming by using StreamingResponse with manual formatting and ThreadPoolExecutor for async DB calls. Fixed Graph endpoint by removing non-existent 'data' column query - now reads from file_path. Fixed Reviews endpoint similarly. All features now working: Live Activity shows connected, Graph displays 100 nodes, Reviews lists decisions with validation status.
